<li id="cite_note-fink11dec10-114">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-fink11dec10_114-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-fink11dec10_114-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20111210195943/http://www.normanfinkelstein.com/reasoned-rejection-of-one-state-position/">"Reasoned rejection of one-state position – Norman G. Finkelstein"</a>. <i>normanfinkelstein.com</i>. December 10, 2011. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.normanfinkelstein.com/reasoned-rejection-of-one-state-position/">the original</a> on December 10, 2011<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">October 4,</span> 2020</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=normanfinkelstein.com&amp;rft.atitle=Reasoned+rejection+of+one-state+position+%E2%80%93+Norman+G.+Finkelstein&amp;rft.date=2011-12-10&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.normanfinkelstein.com%2Freasoned-rejection-of-one-state-position%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANorman+Finkelstein" class="Z3988"></span></span>
