<li id="cite_note-Reynolds2017-125">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Reynolds2017_125-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
