<li id="cite_note-mw16-129">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-mw16_129-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-mw16_129-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFWeiss2016" class="citation web cs1">Weiss, Philip (April 27, 2016). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://mondoweiss.net/2016/04/norman-finkelstein-on-sanders-the-first-intifada-bds-and-ten-years-of-unemployment/">"Norman Finkelstein on Sanders, the first intifada, BDS, and ten years of unemployment"</a>. <i>Mondoweiss</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">October 4,</span> 2020</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Mondoweiss&amp;rft.atitle=Norman+Finkelstein+on+Sanders%2C+the+first+intifada%2C+BDS%2C+and+ten+years+of+unemployment&amp;rft.date=2016-04-27&amp;rft.aulast=Weiss&amp;rft.aufirst=Philip&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fmondoweiss.net%2F2016%2F04%2Fnorman-finkelstein-on-sanders-the-first-intifada-bds-and-ten-years-of-unemployment%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANorman+Finkelstein" class="Z3988"></span></span>
